    <h2>I love travelling!</h2>

    <p>As a creature from another planet, I'm very interested in your different human cultures.</p>

    <p>So far, I've lived and worked in 11 cities, 8 countries and 3 continents, and have visited much more. Definitely less places than I would like to, but I'm always open to move abroad to work in other places and learn more about different aproaches to life!</p>
